name: Shelfed
description:
made in three hours for the trijam

scp 3008 

made you stuck in an ikea where you have to collect boxes and remove the bombs

how to play

push the boxes to the left 

and the bombs to the right

if a bomb goes in the left the counter -5s

if a box goes in the right the counter -1s

a,d and left,right arrows for movement

w and up arrow to jump
